summary: This is a simple replacer for the main menu.
descriptionHtml:
A beautiful Snow Elf to grace your main menu. 
This is a character of mine, and the picture was an in game screenshot which became popular.
Here we see her mourning the loss of her people, and the fate which befell the Falmer.
Simply install with the mod manager of your choice. 
Many thanks to [url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/users/1275801]00m9[/url], from whom I got the main menu mesh.
You can find his fantastic mods here [url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/users/1275801]00m9[/url]
author: Froztee
